1:46:50.250 --> 1:46:51.875
[bell jingles]

1:46:56.166 --> 1:46:58.791
Boy. Girl. Where are you?

1:46:58.875 --> 1:47:01.583
[bell jingling]

1:47:06.083 --> 1:47:08.083
[Malorie] Come with me. Look at me.

1:47:08.625 --> 1:47:10.916
I need you. Just look at me.

1:47:11.000 --> 1:47:13.000
Can I really take off my blindfold?

1:47:13.083 --> 1:47:14.833
-[Malorie] Boy!
-[Boy] It's safe?

1:47:14.916 --> 1:47:16.708
[Malorie] No, that's not me.

1:47:17.875 --> 1:47:20.500
No, no, no. Keep your blindfold on.

1:47:20.583 --> 1:47:22.000
Boy, that's not real.

