1:47:46.625 --> 1:47:50.250
No. No, I'm right here. I'm right here!
Do not take off your blindfold!

1:47:50.333 --> 1:47:51.541
Please listen to me!

1:47:51.625 --> 1:47:52.916
-[Jessica] Malorie.
-What? No.

1:47:53.000 --> 1:47:55.208
-Please open your eyes.
-No. Girl, call out to me.

1:47:55.291 --> 1:47:59.166
-It's just beautiful.
-Call out to me, please. Where are you?

1:47:59.791 --> 1:48:02.708
Boy. Girl. Where are you?
Don't take my children.

1:48:02.791 --> 1:48:04.375
Do not take my children!

1:48:04.458 --> 1:48:06.666
[bell jingling]

1:48:07.583 --> 1:48:09.750
-Oh, baby, keep ringing. Keep ringing.
-[bell jingling]

1:48:09.833 --> 1:48:12.416
Keep ringing, baby.
I'm coming. Keep ringing.

1:48:12.500 --> 1:48:14.958
Come on, keep ringing. Keep ringing.

1:48:15.041 --> 1:48:16.875
Oh, my God. I've got you.

1:48:17.458 --> 1:48:21.416
I've got you. We're good. Where's Girl?
Where's Girl? Where's Girl?

1:48:21.500 --> 1:48:23.666
Girl. Girl! Girl!

1:48:24.250 --> 1:48:25.416
Where's Girl? [grunts]

1:48:26.000 --> 1:48:27.250
