1:48:27.333 --> 1:48:28.500
What?

1:48:28.583 --> 1:48:30.041
She's scared of you.

1:48:30.125 --> 1:48:32.291
[Malorie panting]

1:48:32.375 --> 1:48:33.375
It's okay.

1:48:33.458 --> 1:48:34.291
Uh...

1:48:35.458 --> 1:48:37.250
Oh, I'm so sorry.

1:48:38.250 --> 1:48:40.625
I'm so sorry, sweet girl. I'm so sorry.

1:48:41.666 --> 1:48:44.125
I was wrong.
I shouldn't have been so harsh.

1:48:45.166 --> 1:48:47.291
I shouldn't have stopped you from playing.

1:48:47.833 --> 1:48:54.166
I shouldn't have ended Tom's story
because it wasn't finished.

1:48:54.250 --> 1:48:58.083
When he climbed to the very top
of that giant oak tree,

1:48:58.666 --> 1:49:01.541
he saw the most beautiful things.

1:49:01.625 --> 1:49:05.125
He saw hundreds of children playing games.

1:49:05.208 --> 1:49:06.291
Hundreds.

1:49:06.791 --> 1:49:08.500
And he saw birds...

1:49:09.458 --> 1:49:11.000
all different colored birds,

1:49:11.083 --> 1:49:14.041
and... and he saw us.

1:49:14.625 --> 1:49:16.958
He saw us from the very top.

1:49:17.041 --> 1:49:19.666
He saw us together,
and we have to be together.

1:49:20.375 --> 1:49:22.375
And it's not just a story.

1:49:22.458 --> 1:49:26.458
It's not, because I have
so much I want to show you.

1:49:27.041 --> 1:49:30.708
I have so much I want you to see. Okay?

1:49:30.791 --> 1:49:32.958
But we have to do it together, okay?

1:49:33.041 --> 1:49:36.833
So I just need you
to come to me right now, okay? Please?

1:49:37.333 --> 1:49:38.375
Just come to me.

1:49:38.458 --> 1:49:40.375
Baby, come to me, okay?

1:49:40.458 --> 1:49:41.833
Oh! Ah.

1:49:50.416 --> 1:49:52.333
[Malorie weeps]

1:49:52.416 --> 1:49:55.625
I love you so much.
I love you so much. I love you so much.

1:49:55.708 --> 1:49:57.416
I love you so much.

1:49:57.500 --> 1:50:00.458
We need to find the birds, okay?
Find the birds.

1:50:02.125 --> 1:50:04.208
I want you to listen for the birds, okay?

1:50:07.583 --> 1:50:08.666
Listen for the birds.

1:50:09.625 --> 1:50:11.000
Okay, listen for the birds.

1:50:11.500 --> 1:50:13.000
[birds chirping]

1:50:20.291 --> 1:50:22.708
Listen for the birds.
Just listen for the birds.

1:50:22.791 --> 1:50:24.208
-[Tom] Malorie.
-[gasps]

1:50:30.875 --> 1:50:31.750
[Tom] Malorie.

1:50:31.833 --> 1:50:32.916
[panting]

1:50:35.833 --> 1:50:38.500
Be quiet. Quiet. Quiet. Quiet.

1:50:38.583 --> 1:50:40.916
[Tom] Malorie,
I know you're scared, but it's me.

1:50:43.083 --> 1:50:45.166
Please. Where are you, Mal? I need help!

1:50:46.500 --> 1:50:48.208
Just take a peek and find me.

1:50:48.291 --> 1:50:49.208
[rumbling]

1:50:50.416 --> 1:50:51.666
Come on.

1:50:52.625 --> 1:50:53.625
Come on.

1:50:56.750 --> 1:50:58.583
Go to the birds. Where are the birds?

1:51:03.583 --> 1:51:06.500
Where are the birds?
The birds. Where are the birds?

1:51:06.583 --> 1:51:07.500
That way.

1:51:09.083 --> 1:51:10.291
[distorted voices]

1:51:10.375 --> 1:51:12.625
I can't hear the birds!
I can't hear the birds!

1:51:12.708 --> 1:51:14.541
[Boy] It's too loud. It's too noisy!

1:51:14.625 --> 1:51:17.458
Malorie! It's too loud!

1:51:26.625 --> 1:51:27.583
[birds chirping]

1:51:29.458 --> 1:51:30.833
[Malorie] This way!

1:51:44.250 --> 1:51:46.250
[rumbling]

1:51:52.291 --> 1:51:53.291
[grunts]

1:51:56.000 --> 1:51:57.166
[grunts]

1:51:58.041 --> 1:51:58.875
[rumbling]

1:52:02.208 --> 1:52:03.791
[birds chirping]

1:52:06.708 --> 1:52:07.958
