Let me see your eyes!

1:52:41.583 --> 1:52:42.500
Okay.

1:52:42.583 --> 1:52:43.500
[panting]

1:52:48.875 --> 1:52:49.916
[woman] She's okay.

1:52:51.416 --> 1:52:53.000
She's okay. They're all okay.

1:52:53.625 --> 1:52:54.625
Get Rick.

1:52:55.541 --> 1:52:56.541
It's okay.

1:52:58.458 --> 1:52:59.541
